            "id": "6839d3160a4f35000124e916",
            "title": "Nasdaq Down 100 Points; Chicago PMI Dips In May",
            "description": "<div><div class=\"sc-hSXIdo MtXbD\"><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\">U.S. stocks traded lower this morning, with the Nasdaq Composite falling over 100 points on Friday.</p><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\">Following the market opening Friday, the Dow traded down 0.18% to 42,140.55 while the NASDAQ fell 0.57% to 19,066.89. The S&amp;P 500 also fell, dropping, 0.34% to 5,892.19.</p><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\">Check This Out: <a href=\"https://www.benzinga.com/25/05/45640155/wall-streets-most-accurate-analysts-give-their-take-on-3-materials-stocks-delivering-high-dividend-yields-5\" target=\"_blank\">Wall Street’s Most Accurate Analysts Give Their Take On 3 Materials Stocks Delivering High-Dividend Yields</a></p><!--/$--><!--$--><!--$--><div class=\"sc-exeBjx kjPTmb raptive-ad-placement mx-auto overflow-hidden min-h-[250px] min-w-[300px] raptive-ad-wrapper flex flex-col items-center justify-center\"><div class=\"raptive-ben-content w-full flex items-center justify-center\" id=\"\"></div></div><!--/$--><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\"><strong>Leading and Lagging Sectors</strong><br/><br/>Consumer staples shares jumped by 0.9% on Friday.</p><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\">In trading on Friday, energy stocks fell by 0.9%.</p><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\"><strong>Top Headline</strong></p><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\">The Chicago PMI declined to 40.5 in May versus 44.6 in the previous month.</p><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\"><strong>Equities Trading UP<br/>           </strong></p><!--/$--><!--$--><ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Global Interactive Technologies, Inc.</strong> <span class=\"ticker\" data-exchange=\"NASDAQ\" data-ticker=\"GITS\" style=\"display:inline-block\">GITS</span> shares shot up 149% to $2.41.</li>\n<li>Shares of <strong>Nuburu, Inc. </strong><span class=\"ticker\" data-exchange=\"NYSE\" data-ticker=\"BURU\" style=\"display:inline-block\">BURU</span> got a boost, surging 136% to $0.4735.</li>\n<li><strong>BioLineRx Ltd. </strong><span class=\"ticker\" data-exchange=\"NASDAQ\" data-ticker=\"BLRX\" style=\"display:inline-block\">BLRX</span> shares were also up, gaining 79% to $6.95 after the company said updated results from the pilot phase of its CheMo4METPANC Phase 2 combination trial in pancreatic cancer indicated four of eleven patients remained progression free after more than one year.</li>\n</ul><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\"><strong>Equities Trading DOWN</strong></p><!--/$--><!--$--><ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Babcock &amp; Wilcox Enterprises </strong><span class=\"ticker\" data-exchange=\"NYSE\" data-ticker=\"BWNB\" style=\"display:inline-block\">BWNB</span> shares dropped 33% to $8.74.</li>\n<li>Shares of <strong>Medicus Pharma Ltd. </strong><span class=\"ticker\" data-exchange=\"NASDAQ\" data-ticker=\"MDCX\" style=\"display:inline-block\">MDCX</span> were down 32% to $2.4624.</li>\n<li><strong>CollPlant Biotechnologies Ltd. </strong><span class=\"ticker\" data-exchange=\"NASDAQ\" data-ticker=\"CLGN\" style=\"display:inline-block\">CLGN</span> was down, falling 31% to $3.1201. CollPlant Biotechnologies announced a $3.6 million registered direct offering priced at-the-market under Nasdaq rules.</li>\n</ul><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\"><strong>Latest Startup Investment Opportunities</strong>:</p><!--/$--><!--$--><div class=\"sc-fKJUCN lebKgX block listing-preview-block\"><div class=\"sc-iveMyJ bEQLkz offerings-carousel-wrapper default GalleryCarousel_splide_slidewrap__zHpTC\"><div class=\"sc-iMAVTd gOePzW carousel-container\"><div aria-label=\"Carousel\" class=\"splide\"><div class=\"splide-track-wrapper\"><div class=\"splide__track\"><ul class=\"splide__list\"><li class=\"splide__slide\"><div class=\"sc-jGnrAr dDzYKc listing-preview default\"><div class=\"listing-image-container\"><a data-label=\"Offering Detai